  <brief_title>Laser Iridotomy Versus Surgical Iridectomy in Early Angle Closure</brief_title>
  <official_title>Laser Peripheral Iridotomy Versus Surgical Peripheral Iridectomy in Early Angle Closure:a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
